You're my people,

00:07:03.380 --> 00:07:03.620
too.

00:07:04.640 --> 00:07:06.230
You're Carnegie Mellon people,

00:07:08.570 --> 00:07:10.070
Carnegie Mellon students,

00:07:10.490 --> 00:07:12.230
Carnegie Mellon graduates,

00:07:12.530 --> 00:07:13.400
my people.

00:07:14.420 --> 00:07:14.990
So,

00:07:15.290 --> 00:07:15.979
help me out today.

00:07:16.310 --> 00:07:16.920
I need help.

00:07:20.880 --> 00:07:22.579
So, because I've got to read this,

00:07:22.790 --> 00:07:24.050
and I don't know how it's going to
go.

00:07:24.590 --> 00:07:25.520
So we'll get to see.

