students, girls? Girls, guys,

00:22:09.070 --> 00:22:09.940
these guys,

00:22:09.970 --> 00:22:10.535
girls, whatever. You

00:22:12.250 --> 00:22:13.749
students. Sorry. You had a life

00:22:14.020 --> 00:22:14.860
with your parents,

00:22:15.650 --> 00:22:16.810
then a life at CMU,

00:22:17.530 --> 00:22:19.130
and you're going to have a few more
lives.

00:22:19.870 --> 00:22:20.560
Right now,

00:22:21.580 --> 00:22:22.930
like I did, I think right now,

