y'all have negative balance sheets.

00:22:26.390 --> 00:22:28.610
But you have so much

00:22:28.940 --> 00:22:29.600
upside.

00:22:31.280 --> 00:22:33.110
You all have great opportunities
ahead.

00:22:33.860 --> 00:22:35.120
Don't let anyone,

00:22:35.990 --> 00:22:36.830
anyone,

00:22:38.360 --> 00:22:39.230
tell you different.

00:22:40.350 --> 00:22:42.200
You live in what was,

00:22:42.740 --> 00:22:43.250
is,

00:22:43.550 --> 00:22:44.780
and always will be,

00:22:45.110 --> 00:22:46.460
the land of opportunity

00:22:47.540 --> 00:22:49.279
and the greatest and most generous
country in the

00:22:49.370 --> 00:22:49.670
world.

